VICE power:</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">37</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">DUMP OF SERVICE reboot:</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">38</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">DUMP OF SERVICE screenshot:</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">39</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">DUMP OF SERVICE search:</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">40</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">DUMP OF SERVICE sensor:</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">41</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">DUMP OF SERVICE simphonebook:</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">42</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">DUMP OF SERVICE statusbar:</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">43</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">DUMP OF SERVICE telephony.registry:</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">44</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">DUMP OF SERVICE throttle:</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">45</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">DUMP OF SERVICE usagestats:</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">46</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">DUMP OF SERVICE vibrator:</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">47</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">DUMP OF SERVICE wallpaper:</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">48</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">DUMP OF SERVICE wifi:</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">49</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">DUMP OF SERVICE window:</span></span></code></pre>\n<p>eg:<br>\n1.得到电池的所有信息</p>\n<pre class=\"hljs code-block\"><code class=\"language-bash\"><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:1\">1</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">adb shell dumpsys battery</span></span></code></pre>\n<p>2.得到wifi的所有信息</p>\n<pre class=\"hljs code-block\"><code class=\"language-bash\"><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:1\">1</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">adb shell dumpsys wifi</span></span></code></pre>\n<p>3.得到cpu的所有信息</p>\n<pre class=\"hljs code-block\"><code class=\"language-bash\"><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:1\">1</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">adb shell dumpsys cpuinfo</span></span></code></pre>\n<p>4.得到总的存储情况</p>\n<pre class=\"hljs code-block\"><code class=\"language-bash\"><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:1\">1</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">adb shell dumpsys meminfo</span></span></code></pre>\n<p>5.得到某应用的存储情况</p>\n<pre class=\"hljs code-block\"><code class=\"language-bash\"><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:1\">1</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">adb shell dumpsys meminfo <span class=\"hljs-string\">&#x27;your apps package name&#x27;</span></span></span></code></pre>\n<p>6.得到所有的服务列表</p>\n<pre class=\"hljs code-block\"><code class=\"language-bash\"><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:1\">1</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">adb shell service list</span></span></code></pre>\n<p>7.得到所有的账户列表</p>\n<pre class=\"hljs code-block\"><code class=\"language-bash\"><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:1\">1</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">adb shell dumpsys account</span></span></code></pre>\n<p>8.获得某子命令的帮助信息</p>\n<pre class=\"hljs code-block\"><code class=\"language-bash\"><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:1\">1</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">adb shell dumpsys account -h</span></span></code></pre>\n<p>参考:<br>\n<a href=\"https://stackoverflow.com/questions/11201659/whats-the-android-adb-shell-dumpsys-tool-and-what-are-its-benefits\">What’s the Android ADB shell “dumpsys” tool and what are its benefits?</a></p>\n","rawMarkdown":"","plainText":"","toc":[],"slugForSearch":"25303996","comments":true,"math":false,"mermaid":false}}